<section class="foundation-demo" aria-label="透视与景深基础示意图">
  <div class="foundation-demo__grid">
    <div class="foundation-demo__card">
      <div class="foundation-demo__badge">透视看站位</div>
      <div class="foundation-demo__scene foundation-demo__scene--perspective">
        <div class="foundation-demo__near">近</div>
        <div class="foundation-demo__mid">中</div>
        <div class="foundation-demo__far">远</div>
      </div>
      <p>你离主体越近，近处和远处的差异就越明显。透视变化首先来自站位，不是先来自镜头数字。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="foundation-demo__card">
      <div class="foundation-demo__badge">景深看层次</div>
      <div class="foundation-demo__scene foundation-demo__scene--depth">
        <div class="foundation-demo__blur foundation-demo__blur--front">前景</div>
        <div class="foundation-demo__focus">主体</div>
        <div class="foundation-demo__blur foundation-demo__blur--back">背景</div>
      </div>
      <p>景深的重点不是“虚不虚”，而是你让谁清楚、让谁退后。手机也能先把这个判断练出来。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

